[
  {
    "task": "Extract action items from the transcript",
    "owner": "unassigned",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "The meeting discusses the impact of COVID-19 on the tourism industry in Waikato, the response plan of Tourism Waikato, and the financial situation of Hamilton Airport."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a three-tiered response plan for the tourism industry",
    "owner": "Jason",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We have a what we call a three-tiered response plan. Obviously, this is no similar to everyone else right now. We have a mitigate um process which we're currently in now. We then have a restart phase, and then we have a reimagine phase."
  },
  {
    "task": "Conduct scenario modeling for the airport company",
    "owner": "Mark Morgan",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We've completed significant cost reductions in the business that's right across the business so that's um major cost reductions in our expense lines uh reductions uh pretty much across our business in terms of payroll uh anything up to a 20% reduction."
  },
  {
    "task": "Review and revise the Statement of Intent (SOI) for LASS",
    "owner": "Peter",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We are looking to be bolder, more disruptive to enable you to help you transform how you and other Waikato councils operate."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a green financing program for LGFA",
    "owner": "Andrew",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We are intending to offer green financing to councils. So remembering that it's not LGFA that is doing things with the money. We're just sort of leaning up so we sort of sit in the middle."
  },
  {
    "task": "Reforecast the financial report for Waipa District Council",
    "owner": "Nada",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "A huge effort has gone on right across some across council in the last um, in the last two or three weeks, um, to, um, yeah, to reforecast and you should see the results of that reforecast and you should have a obviously a quite a different, um, forecast column in the next, um, financial report you see."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop health and safety protocols for COVID-19",
    "owner": "Bev",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We're working up some really good protocols around how to keep them all safe."
  }
]

